info.description:
The top banner ads on Penny Arcade are getting through the old v2 style, so I made this modification. I just added a single line to tyler's stlye. I changed this line:
#adhoriz, #advert { display: none !important }
to this:
#adhoriz, #advert, #funding-h { display: none !important }

style.css:
@namespace url(http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml);
@-moz-document domain("penny-arcade.com") {
#adhoriz, #advert, #funding-h { display: none !important }

#news { width: auto !important; }

#news .newspost .postheader {
    float: left !important;
    padding: 3px 0px 0px 5px !important;
    }

}
